node.text:
Hello everyone here are some Videos from Different places in Switzerland 🇨🇭 Did you hike somewhere over the weekend?
@amir_asani13 shows you guys some beautiful Swiss Landscapes Tag someone you’d like to visit these places with.
Have a beautiful week everyone 

Put these places on your bucket list for your next visit 📜

📍 Switzerland 🇨🇭
🎥 @amir_asani13 

1.Grindelwald Mountain Cart
2.Mürren 
3.Hüttnersee
4.Siegriswil
5.Appenzell
6.Grindelwald 
7.Stechelberg
8.Bernese Oberland 
9.Canton Luzern
10.Grindelwald First
